### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Generate Itinerary
POST http://localhost:3000/api/itinerary/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "arrival": {
    "date": "2026-04-01",
    "location": "Barcelona, Spain"
  },
  "departure": {
    "date": "2026-04-07",
    "location": "Barcelona, Spain"
  },
  "desiredAttractions": [
    "Sagrada Familia",
    "Park Güell",
    "Gothic Quarter",
    "Las Ramblas",
    "Montjuïc"
  ],
  "travelPace": "moderate",
  "interests": ["architecture", "food", "culture"],
  "budget": "mid-range",
  "notes": "First time in Barcelona, prefer walkable areas"
}
